        "description": "Your reps have been burned. They've shared links that went nowhere. They've driven sales and gotten no credit. They've watched their commissions disappear into attribution black holes. Now they don't trust your tracking, so they've stopped sharing—or worse, they're using workarounds you can't see. These are the questions companies ask when they realize broken attribution is costing them millions in lost revenue.",
